---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | AIToolPick"
  description="AIToolPick helps you find the right AI and productivity tools for your workflow through honest comparisons and reviews."
>
  <div class="about-content">
    <h1>About AIToolPick</h1>

    <p>
      AIToolPick helps you find the right tools for your workflow. With hundreds of AI and productivity
      tools launching every month, choosing the right one can feel overwhelming. We make it simple.
    </p>

    <p>
      Our side-by-side comparisons break down the features, pricing, pros, and cons of the most popular
      tools so you can make an informed decision without spending hours on research.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Cover</h2>
    <p>
      We focus on tools that help you get work done: project management, AI assistants, design tools,
      note-taking apps, automation platforms, and more. Every comparison is based on real features and
      publicly available pricing.
    </p>

    <h2>Our Approach</h2>
    <p>
      We believe in transparency. Our comparisons are data-driven and regularly updated. We highlight
      both the strengths and weaknesses of every tool because no single tool is perfect for everyone.
    </p>

    <p>
      Some links on this site may be affiliate links, which help support the site at no extra cost to you.
      This never influences our recommendations.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Have a suggestion or found an error? We'd love to hear from you.
      Reach out at <a href="mailto:hello@aitoolpick.com">hello@aitoolpick.com</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
